Recipe: #024 - Fruit Juice Smoothie DIPA - Citra/Amarillo DIPA
Brewer: 
Asst Brewer: 
Style: Double IPA
TYPE: All Grain
Taste: (30.0) 2017-02-20
Aroma: Tons of aroma. Citrus, Fruit, Vitamin C, Tropical
Apperance: Wicked Orange with some golden hues. Foam hugs to the side of the glass.
Taste: Citrus, Tropical, Fruit, Upfront clean bitterness, followed by fruit juice. Bitterness lingers but is pleasant.

Won 3rd place 2017 Yeastwranglers competition

Recipe Specifications
--------------------------
Boil Size: 31.08 l
Post Boil Volume: 27.08 l
Batch Size (fermenter): 25.00 l   
Bottling Volume: 23.30 l
Estimated OG: 1.077 SG
Estimated Color: 7.4 SRM
Estimated IBU: 132.4 IBUs
Brewhouse Efficiency: 53.00 %
Est Mash Efficiency: 55.1 %
Boil Time: 60 Minutes

